              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute differential cross section for H-2(g,p)n",
                " reaction has been determined for lab angles  of  20,",
                " 45,  65,  90, 115, 135, and 160 degrees, through the",
                " excitation energy  range  from  17  -  25  MeV.  The",
                " estimated  experimental uncertainty in cross section",
                " values is 6%."
              ]
            }
          ],
